Presumably this is a dvd video of that event??

Campus Party is a yearly event where people take its own home computer/consoles to the event and play for days. It is the biggest lanparty in Spain. This year Microsoft made a presentation of its comming Xbox 360 in the Campus Party, and that is what this video is. Oh, and NO people could not play in the Xbox 360.
